Workflow
========================================================
type: section

Everyday git
========================================================

1. work on files
2. commit to repository
    - adding files
    
    ```
    $ git add [file]
    ```
    - commit + message
    
    ```
    $ git commit -m "edit [file]"
    ```


Once in a while git
========================================================

3. tagging

  ```
  $ git tag [v*.*.*] -m "[newest version]"
  ```
  
5. time travelling

  ```
  $ git checkout v1.0
  $ git checkout master
  ```

6. branching


