GitHub
========================================================

- remote repositories
- **free** for open source projects (fully public!)
- private repositories (commercial)
- manage development (teams, tasks, milestones, wikis)

Alternatives: [Bitbucket](https://bitbucket.org/) (free private for small teams), [GitLab Cloud](https://about.gitlab.com/gitlab-com/)(unlimited free private), and more

