2 | tagging
========================================================
type: sub-section

in same repository:

1. tag
2. edit content 
3. add and commit
5. check history: `git log` 
6. checkout tag
7. return to latest version

3 | GitHub
========================================================
type: sub-section

1. create a git repository on Github.
2. clone to Local PC: <br> `git clone https://github.com`
3. generate content
4. add and commit
5. push
6. edit online
7. pull


4 | Collaboration
========================================================
type: sub-section

1. clone shared project
3. create a file
4. add, commit, push
5. assign a task
6. check your tasklist
7. pull repository
8. fullfill task
9. add, commit, push
10. check out progress on tasks

etc.: Milestones, Wiki